description.en:
Shiberus Inu is a community driven,fully decentralised cryptocurrency, powered by the collective efforts of all the Inu breeds combined.

The legend of Shiberus Inu was created as a community response to the financial system with strong commitment to empower the people and help the ones in need.

Shiberus Inu's power is generated by the loyalty of his followers and rewards his holders by a 2% redistribution from transactions.
